<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:120%;"><strong><a href="https://redcircle.com/shows/5af1a111-e948-475f-9f7d-913f572ddd88/episodes/bbf50adf-72f6-4b02-8b69-be021c913361" target="_blank">Listen to the episode here!</a></strong></span></p>
